meta.executedQueryString:
data = from(bucket: "metrics")
  |> range(start: -30d)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "request_status_time")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "request_status_time")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["status"] == "RUNNING")
  |> group()

p99 = data |> quantile(q: 0.99) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.0")
p991 = data |> quantile(q: 0.991) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.1")
p992 = data |> quantile(q: 0.992) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.2")
p993 = data |> quantile(q: 0.993) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.3")
p994 = data |> quantile(q: 0.994) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.4")
p995 = data |> quantile(q: 0.995) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.5")
p996 = data |> quantile(q: 0.996) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.6")
p997 = data |> quantile(q: 0.997) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.7")
p998 = data |> quantile(q: 0.998) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.8")
p999 = data |> quantile(q: 0.999) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p99.9")
p1000 = data |> quantile(q: 1.000) |> set(key: "percentile", value: "p100.0")

union(tables: [p99, p991, p992, p993, p994, p995, p996, p997, p998, p999, p1000])
  |> group()
  |> keep(columns: ["percentile", "_value"])
  |> rename(columns: {_value: "runtime_seconds"})
